  characterName: Cowtana
  frames:
  - characterDialogue: Chef!
    responses:
    - ...
  - characterDialogue: Thank goodness you made it.
    responses:
    - ...
  - characterDialogue: We've landed on that mysterious Halo.
    responses:
    - ...
  - characterDialogue: Apparently this was built by the Foreskinrunners, though for
      what purpose I'm not entirely sure.
    responses:
    - ...
  - characterDialogue: When activated it'll either kill all the Cowvenant, or destroy
      itself. I'm not totally sure, the facility schematics are giving me a lot of
      **mixed signals**.
    responses:
    - ...
  - characterDialogue: Either way, our best bet is to activate it (just for shiz
      and giggles).
    responses:
    - Sounds like a good plan to me!
